  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下工业物联网的数据流。核心是从MQTT Broker到TelemetryStream，再到PLC Logic这个链条。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，MQTT Broker作为数据入口。我注意到您提到了两个Broker节点？Audit和Code都是MQTT Broker吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Audit和Code都是IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker，代表两个不同的Broker实例，一个用于审计采集，一个用于主数据通道。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Audit和Code都标注为IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker。那TelemetryStream也有两个？Bail和Define？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Bail和Define都是IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream，分别是实时流和定义配置流。Barg是唯一的PLC Logic节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我来画一下流向：Audit指向Define，Code也指向Define，然后Define指向Barg，Bail也指向Barg。这样主数据通道就清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Barg到Bail应该还有个回流，PLC Logic需要反向控制TelemetryStream。另外我看到还有Risk、Signal、Press这些节点，它们是独立的外部信号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Barg到Bail的回流。Risk、Signal、Place这三个节点我理解为外部输入，Risk指向Signal，Signal指向Barg，Place指向Press？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "Press应该是独立的终点，不是被指向的。Place到Press是一条完整的控制链路，表示放置操作触发按压信号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "修正了，Place到Press是一条边。现在整体结构是：双Broker汇入双TelemetryStream，都流向PLC Logic，PLC有回流，外加Risk-Signal-Barg的风险链路，以及Place-Press的独立控制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "布局上用LR横向流吧，从左到右：Risk、Place这些外部信号在左侧，Broker层，然后TelemetryStream，最右是PLC Logic，回流线可以绕回来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Place",
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Bail",
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。横向布局已调整，所有节点和流向都按您要求配置好了。Audit和Code作为MQTT Broker入口，Define和Bail作为TelemetryStream处理层，Barg作为PLC Logic核心，外部Risk-Signal和Place-Press两条控制链路也清晰标注。",
